BNP Paribas in JapanBNP Paribas has long-term relationships with leading organisations and deep knowledge of the Japan market. The history of BNP Paribas in Japan dates back to 1867 when Comptoir National d’Escompte de Paris, the predecessor to BNP, opened a branch office in Yokohama.
