BNPP Investment Partners Japan appoints new CEO
By The Asset

               Asset manager BNP Paribas Investment Partners Japan Ltd. (BNPP IPJ ) has named Tino Moorrees as CEO and president. He replaced Daniel Klein, who has been appointed deputy CEO of BNP Paribas Investment Partners - North America.

              



